{"tid":949491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］美國國防部長馬蒂斯辭職","createTime":"2018-12-20T23:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T16:36:17.000Z","uid":112221,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"50de7784f415a0366ded661d8f6accdac297ec25","tid":949491,"uid":112221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T23:32:17.000Z","msg":"US Defence Secretary Jim Mattis will be retiring &rdquo;with distinction&ldquo; at the end of February, President Donald Trump announced on Thursday.<br />\nMr Trump tweeted that General Mattis &rdquo;was a great help to me in getting allies and other countries to pay their share of military obligations&ldquo;.<br />\nIt comes a day after the president&rsquo;s controversial announcement that all US troops would be withdrawn from Syria.<br />\nMr Trump did not name a successor, but said one would be appointed shortly.<br />\nIn his resignation letter, Gen Mattis described his views on &rdquo;treating allies with respect&ldquo; and using &rdquo;all the tools of American power to provide for the common defence&ldquo;.<br />\n&rdquo;Because you have the right to have a secretary of defence whose views are better aligned with yours on these and other subjects, I believe it is right for me to step down,&ldquo; Gen Mattis wrote.<br />\n<br />\nMr Trump announced his decision to withdraw the 2,000 US troops from Syria on Wednesday, asserting that the Islamic State (IS) group had been defeated there.<br />\nThe news, which was met with strong criticism, is at odds with Mr Mattis&rsquo; position, who had warned that an early withdrawal from the country would be a &rdquo;strategic blunder&ldquo;.<br />\nUS troops have helped rid much of Syria&lsquo;s north-east of the jihadist group, but pockets of fighters remain.<br />\nThe White House would not give a timescale for the withdrawal but defence officials quoted by the New York Times said President Trump wanted it done within 30 days.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bbc.in/2Cs9Y7P\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbbc.in%2F2Cs9Y7P&d=0YVBAqgRK1L8n%2BFuuCtTf4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=1c5c6b6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://bbc.in/2Cs9Y7P</a>"},{"pid":"ff71df6fa0ea48d3889998bc58d022b099c7a005","tid":949491,"uid":42921,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T23:34:52.000Z","msg":"Mad dog都唔夠trump 仔玩丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc262385667a8770d9d9ceca5fc550fa77c733c","tid":949491,"uid":102096,"like":7,"dislike":16,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T23:44:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7722c17e45707996f4c2012ef54af88b3a49539","tid":949491,"uid":18948,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T23:54:06.000Z","msg":"Trump 明明話請個喺一方面最叻嘅人跟住放手畀佢搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0057469f7cc6ea254ff795a2963518dc0dce313","tid":949491,"uid":61660,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"e7722c17e45707996f4c2012ef54af88b3a49539","tid":949491,"uid":18948,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T23:54:06.000Z","msg":"Trump 明明話請個喺一方面最叻嘅人跟住放手畀佢搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T23:56:42.000Z","msg":"我落完柯打咪放手俾你搞<br />\n有咩問題"},{"pid":"bbfcaa3e2a034d96f14b5c85fd685875a1044515","tid":949491,"uid":34896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0057469f7cc6ea254ff795a2963518dc0dce313","tid":949491,"uid":61660,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"e7722c17e45707996f4c2012ef54af88b3a49539","tid":949491,"uid":18948,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T23:54:06.000Z","msg":"Trump 明明話請個喺一方面最叻嘅人跟住放手畀佢搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T23:56:42.000Z","msg":"我落完柯打咪放手俾你搞<br />\n有咩問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T00:05:58.000Z","msg":"雜總<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2x